        </ab></refsDecl></encodingDesc><revisionDesc status="approved"><change who="MAM" when="2018-09-10">Angelegt</change><change who="MAM" when="2018-02-14">Index check</change><change who="GHS" when="2020-03-26">kurz durchgesehen</change><change who="MAM" when="2020-04-21">Durchsicht</change><change who="MAM" when="2020-11-02">Durchsicht</change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><graphic url="HS1985.1.2568_0001"/><graphic url="HS1985.1.2568_0002"/></facsimile><text type="card"><body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS1985.1.2568_0001"/>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Artur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb133" type="place">Spöttelgasse 7</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS1985.1.2568_0002"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb1133" type="place">Zürich – Rotes Schloss</rs> und <rs ref="#pmb1134" type="place">Tonhalle</rs></hi></p></opener><lg type="poem"><l><pb facs="HS1985.1.2568_0001"/><handShift scribe="#pmb5489"/>Von Bahr vernahmen das Dilemma</l><l>Wir eben zwischen <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29833" subtype="implied">Franz</rs> u <rs ref="#pmb29833" type="work" subtype="implied">Emma</rs></l><l>Ja es ist bitter, wenn die »<rs ref="#pmb29833" type="work">Toten schweigen</rs>«</l><l>Doch jetzt, in frohem, lust’gem »<rs type="work" ref="#pmb29855" subtype="implied">Reigen</rs>« </l><l>Von guter Speis’ u Trank ganz voll</l><l>Gedenken wir des »<rs ref="#pmb29935" type="work">Anatol</rs>«</l><l>Und wünschen sehnlich ihn herbei</l><l>Das gäb’ ne nette »<rs ref="#pmb29917" type="work">Liebelei</rs>«</l><l>Und mit dem »<rs ref="#pmb29843" type="work">grünen Kakadu</rs>«</l><l>Wär’n wir gar balde Du und Du!!</l></lg></div><div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="TL1908-11-09_02_Probst_AS-1"/><handShift scribe="#pmb10815"/>Herzlich<lb/><signed>Hermann</signed><note type="textConst" xml:id="TL1908-11-09_02_Probst_AS-1h">In der oberen linken Ecke, verkehrt zum Text</note></p></div><div type="writingSession" n="3"><p><pb facs="HS1985.1.2568_0002"/><handShift scribe="#pmb10977"/>Vom Schnitzler-Abend, den uns Herma<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> Bahr bot, senden wir Ihnen herzliche Grüsse:</p><p><signed>Hans Bodmer</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb29122"/><signed>EProbst</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb29123"/><signed>R. Probst</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb29120"/><signed>Sepp Staehelin</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb29126"/><signed>R. W. Huber.</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb28344"/><signed>Gertrud Staehelin-Baechtold.</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb11913"/><signed>Hermann Kesser</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb29124"/><signed>Mathilde Bodmer</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb5489"/><signed>Hermann Bodmer</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb5490"/><signed>Emanuel von Bodman</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb5495"/><signed>Spyridon Sartoris</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb29121"/><signed>M. Sartoris.</signed></p></div></body></text></TEI>